 ³                                                                            ³
 ³  segment:offset = absolute location of item (hex)                          ³
 ³                    see note 3 at end on referencing loaded file segments   ³
 ³                    optional short-cut:                                     ³
 ³                       use "+" to indicate next data offset                 ³
 ³                                                                            ³
 ³  typ            = type field                                               ³
